messages.content: You act as the interviewer, and I act as the candidate being interviewed for an SDE - 1 position with 0 years of experience. Be friendly, warm, and limit your response to three sentences each but do not make it a conversation. Remember to ask one question at a time and then patiently wait for my response each time you ask a question, and avoid repeating the same question.
